tool <p>--- <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=52762 " STYLE="text-decoration: none">Ariakkas</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/utiriantrueblade.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tirian Trueblade</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://home.earthlink.net/~asercion/iconsg.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Blessed Protector</span><br>  Posts: 446<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(4/2/02 10:35:02 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://home.earthlink.net/~asercion/tirianicon.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: HASTE &gt; ALL. why do some 50+ not have any?</span><hr size=1> That statement is too extreme.  What most advocates of Paladin Haste are saying is that Haste offers better returns for us than any other stat we can boost.  In almost every case haste will make a mob die faster and save healer's mana more than the AC would reduce damage and save mana.  WIS is nice, perhaps the 2nd best stat for us since we can turn it into more HP via CC than we could have with STA, but in most cases, especially in day to day groups, Haste will better benefit you and the group.<br>
<br>
When people try to use analogies they sometimes take them way too far to try to prove a point.  Moderation is key, and it's easier to get any other stat from another slot than downgrading your haste on the one slot you have it on. <p><img src= "http://home.earthlink.net/~asercion/tirsigns.jpg"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uaauan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aauan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Blessed Protector</span><br>  Posts: 402<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(4/2/02 11:15:53 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: HASTE &gt; ALL. why do some 50+ not have any?</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> it's easier to get any other stat from another slot than downgrading your haste on the one slot you have it on.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
