<br>
Three basic weapons...<br>
<br>
A 35/40 weapon, ratio of 0.875<br>
A 32/35 weapon, ratio of 0.914<br>
A 20/20 weapon, ratio of 1.000<br>
<br>
With no Haste except Valor of Marr (25%)<br>
<br>
A 35/40 weapon becomes 35/32, ratio of 1.094<br>
A 32/35 weapon becomes 32/28, ratio of 1.143<br>
A 20/20 weapon becomes 20/16, ratio of 1.250<br>
<br>
With cheap PoA Haste of 16% &amp; Valor of Marr<br>
<br>
A 35/40 weapon becomes 35/28.37, ratio of 1.234<br>
A 32/35 weapon becomes 32/24.82, ratio of 1.289<br>
A 20/20 weapon becomes 20/14.18, ratio of 1.410<br>
<br>
With an FBSS for 22% &amp; Valor of Marr<br>
<br>
A 35/40 weapon becomes 35/27.21, ratio of 1.286<br>
A 32/35 weapon becomes 32/23.81, ratio of 1.344<br>
A 20/20 weapon becomes 20/13.61, ratio of 1.470<br>
<br>
With Dragon Haste (41%) &amp; Valor of Marr<br>
<br>
A 35/40 weapon becomes 35/24.10, ratio of 1.452<br>
A 32/35 weapon becomes 32/21.08, ratio of 1.518<br>
A 20/20 weapon becomes 20/12.05, ratio of 1.660<br>
<br>
