<br>
You may find that buying a better weapon will serve you many times better than buying better Haste. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ueiago.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Eiago</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Wandering Knight</span><br>  Posts: 214<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(4/2/02 2:36:39 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: HASTE &gt; ALL. why do some 50+ not have any?</span><hr size=1> Ratio is not a determining factor.   Damage per second is.  There are a number of formulas floating around.  Use one of those and you will see a linear increase in damage for the weapons.<br>
